<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title || 'Login - IT Care' %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="Login ke sistem helpdesk internal IT Care">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="auth-page">
  <%- include('../partials/flash') %>

  <div class="auth-shell">
    <div class="auth-grid">
      <section class="auth-side">
        <div>
          <div class="sidebar-brand-link sidebar-logo">
            <span class="brand-mark"><i class="bi bi-grid-1x2-fill"></i></span>
            <span>
              <span class="brand-name">IT<span>Care</span></span>
              <span class="brand-caption">Internal helpdesk workspace</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="auth-kicker">Helpdesk Internal</div>
          <h1>Masuk ke dashboard operasional IT yang lebih rapi.</h1>
          <p>Kelola tiket, pantau penugasan teknisi, dan tindak lanjuti permintaan internal dalam satu alur kerja yang ringkas.</p>
          <ul class="auth-points">
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2"></i><span>Tracking status yang jelas untuk admin, teknisi, dan karyawan</span></li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2"></i><span>Tampilan data yang fokus pada tiket, bukan dekorasi template</span></li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2"></i><span>Laporan operasional tetap tersusun tanpa mengubah alur backend</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="auth-card">
        <div class="auth-header">
          <div class="sidebar-brand-link sidebar-logo">
            <span class="brand-mark logo-icon"><i class="bi bi-grid-1x2-fill"></i></span>
            <span>
              <span class="brand-name">IT<span>Care</span></span>
              <span class="brand-caption">Akses akun Anda</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <h2>Login</h2>
          <p class="auth-subtitle">Gunakan akun kerja Anda untuk masuk ke sistem helpdesk.</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/login" method="POST">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label-custom" for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" class="form-control-custom" placeholder="admin@itcare.id" required autocomplete="email">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label-custom" for="password">Password</label>
            <div class="input-shell">
              <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control-custom" placeholder="Masukkan password" required autocomplete="current-password">
              <button type="button" class="btn-icon-app" data-password-toggle="#password" aria-label="Tampilkan password">
                <i class="bi bi-eye"></i>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary-app btn-block">Masuk</button>
        </form>

        <div class="auth-link-row">
          Belum punya akun? <a href="/register">Daftar di sini</a>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-demo">
          <strong>Akun demo</strong>
          Admin: <code>admin@itcare.id</code><br>
          Teknisi: <code>teknisi@itcare.id</code><br>
          Karyawan: <code>karyawan@itcare.id</code><br>
          Password: <code>password</code>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
